phrases: Why do you dig?
Because a new world awaits on the other side.
I will get to that new world!
Here I come, girls' locker room!
The girls' locker room!
What is this?
Here they are, get'them while they are hot!
Hey, pictures from the field observation trip!
When did you take these, anyway?
Let us just say I mix business with pleasure.
I will take one of Shrade!
Here you go.
Man, I look awful in this one.
Hey, here is a good one of you.
Yep, that is a good one.
You buying that one, Amata?
Would not you rather have a real live girl instead of a picture?
H-Hey!
Amata, you will really fly for anyone!
No!
Um, go ahead and take it.
They are all over you, stud.
Cut that out.
Can I have this photo?
That one?
I guess.
That will be 500 kowloons.
Thanks.
Huh?
Who is that of?
Um...
Just let me see!
Amata?
Amata and Andy?
I would not have thought of that...
Yo, my hole digging bro!
You will never guess what I just found!
What?
Unless I am very much mistaken, this is the Book of Twin Stars!
The Book of Twin Stars?
I have heard of it.
According to the legend, whoever holds that book can take full control of the forbidden Aquarion.
The green cat is right.
Neo-Deava has been looking for this thing since it was founded.
How did you find it, then?
Yeah, where was it?
You see, I was digging a hole to
Look, that is not important right now.
Chairman Crea!
Is not it time you told us the truth?
What do you mean?
You must have found something important if you have returned from your journey.
Important?
Oh, I forgot!
This is for everyone to share.
That is not what we mean!
Do not you like it?
That is not the issue here!
They cannot see it with their eyes.
The book will only open for eyes that cannot see.
So if the verb is conjugated like so...
R, ry... ribbit ribbit?
What does that mean?
Damn it, why did not I pay attention in lit class?
Dude, Amata, help me out here.
Kay.
Um, d... dig... digging?
I have to tell him I am sorry.
Mikono's sorry for what?
This is how it is done!
What are you doing?
Socks must be white!
What?
It is the first line.
He spent all night on it.
This is Chapter 23, verse 1 of the way to unlocking Aquarion's full potential.
What do socks have to do with Aquarion?
Well, this is just my hypothesis, but...
The wisdom of ancient wrestlers states that fighters who lost their shoes were at a disadvantage.
This shows us that feet are one of the most important things that regulate our bodies.
The color of the cloth that wraps such an vital center of the body is a deep matter.
Cloth wrapping vital parts, you say?
It is got a teal border.
What color do you think I am wearing?
Come on, you guys, this is serious!
We are talking about ancient documents here!
Huh?
What do people see in her?
What is this about ancient documents?
Andy says he found one.
Let me see it.
Here...
Mix, can you read that?
Ancient literature is my thing.
Um...
Top buttons must be buttoned.
What?
Top buttons?
No hair that grows past the eyebrows.
Hair?
No dyed hair.
Skirts must reach at least 5cm below the knee.
No running in the halls.
Wait, are not these...
Ancient school rules.
This could be some student's handbook.
What is the matter with him?
To find the most powerful Rare Igura.
We must go to Vega once more.
We have found many Rare Iguras thus far, but the dimensional transference
has either killed them or made them useless to us.
I would be happy with just Alisia.
Jin, this is about the fate of all Altair.
At first, baby girls quit being born on our planet.
Then our women began dying due to an unknown disease.
Eventually, only men remained on Altair.
This is not an invasion of Vega.
We mean only to ensure the survival of our species.
We must find the most powerful Rare Igura, strong enough to survive interdimensional travel intact,
and make her into our true Eve,
the bride who will bear the next generation of Altair.
There is a good chance that the strongest of the Rare Iguras pilots the Machine Angel.
I understand, High Commander Izumo.
I will go down there myself this time instead of piloting by remote.
Go, Jin.
Last son of Altair.
I will dial up the optical sensors...
and I will focus on solid ammo so I do not end up like last time.
Better take some infiltrator ammo too.
Add some heavy armor on top, and...
I have got a perfect, flawless shield of iron.
Man, I made a total ass of myself.
I do not know, an ancient school handbook is a pretty big find itself.
We can donate it to the Neo-Kowloon Museum!
Those old guys sure sweat the small stuff.
Rules for the length of your hair and skirt?
You are wrong!
We can learn from the lessons of history!
Neo-Deava should take the wisdom of the ancients and strengthen its own rules!
What?
I have always thought that your clothes are too revealing, Zessica!
Have you not thought about guarding yourself from the gaze of those boys?
Really?
You think so?
To begin with, what do you think the scriptures say about showing your belly?
You may as well be walking around in just your underwear!
Just her underwear...
Let us try and fix what we can with a few quick rules.
Zessica, there will be no more exposing yourself from now on!
You are treating me like some kind of creep!
Amata, do you think it is bad that you can see my belly?
Well, I mean, not your...
Never have to guess what he is thinking.
Shush?
Do you think guys like girls who wear flashy clothes?
Oh, so you do have clothes like that.
Zessica!
Let me see.
You could show off more.
I think this would look good on you.
I am not like you!
Abductors detected in the Neo-Kowloon area.
Come and get me, Machine Angel.
He will start attacking Neo-Kowloon if we make him wait.
He is not here to abduct people this time.
Fudo, what do you think their goal is?
Heavy Armor Radius Gniss.
Send out Aquarion!
The head is Amata!
With Zessica and Mikono!
Mikono?
But she...
Here I go!
Vector Z, launching!
Vector Y, launching!
Vector X, launching!
Approaching the enemy Abductor!
Get ready, Mikono!
Defensive Union!
Go, Aquarion!
Aquarion Evol!
W-What should I do?
Mikono...
This ends right here, Abductor!
Infinity Punch!
He is tough!
You hit me with that before.
I am not falling for the same thing again.
These are the Rare Iguras?
Pff.
They are light years below Silvie.
Stop it, Jin!
Get back here!
Keep your hands off her!
That is my wench!
Your voice is so ugly.
I know you can cry out more beautifully.
Feel the jealousy, Kagura.
Feel it harder.
Feel the pain of having the one you love stolen away.
Drink it deeply.
Let us see how powerful you Rare Iguras are.
No damage to Aquarion's external armor!
But it is having an effect on the Elements!
He is using infiltrator ammunition?
He is creating shockwaves that resonate through Aquarion, thus dealing damage directly within it...
Mikono!
Their Union rate is plummeting rapidly!
The Union is breaking!
Do not look away.
Watch closely.
Jin is violating your very own Rare Igura.
Stop!
Stop iiit!!
Pathetic.
There is no way one of those weaklings could possibly be our true Eve.
The Element suits have been heavily damaged!
We have to do something or the shock is going to go right to their bodies!
Mikono!
I cannot watch this!
Element Change me!
Let me go, High Commander!
Zessica, dodge it!
What just happened?
I can feel the missiles in the air!
I felt them on my skin!
How is Zessica's machine doing that?
Fudo, what does this mean?
As people get naked, their senses get sharper.
Rip off your clothes, let down your guard,
and you will sense your enemy's moves with perfect precision.
So the less I am wearing, the better I will be able to dodge?
But we cannot possibly do that!
This is not the time to be modest!
Zessica!
I can do it too!
Mikono, not you too!
Mikono and Zessica's mind levels are rising!
They are at a Union-capable level!
Right now!
Union!
The head is Zessica Wong!
Unguarded Union!
Go, Aquarion!
My skin feels so sensitive...
I can feel it all over my body...
So intense!
Aquarion Spada!
I can feel Amata looking at me...
I am so embarrassed!
Mikono's mind level is still rising!
But why?
She knows someone is looking at her, so her body is hot and bothered.
I understand.
It is okay.
You do not have to be embarrassed.
Does not matter if you have Unioned.
Just admit defeat already!
Here they come!
My senses are incredibly keen now...
I can feel them all perfectly!
They dodged?
More!
More!
Zessica's spirit level is at an all-time high!
I will do it too!
I am embarrassed... but!
Their sonata is so powerful
that I cannot possibly play it.
A heart-pounding battle unbound from the chains of modesty!
Let your skin heat up!
Let your body burst forth!
Take this!
No Guard!
Attack!
It is game over for me.
But how could I lose to something as stupid as that?
Yes!
Sorry!
But why am I embarrassed?
The best defense is a good offense.
Dropping your guard is the ultimate weapon.
That is a disgusting and perverted strategy!
I will not stand for it!
Humans are all born naked.
But that strategy is a double-edged sword.
In exchange for perfect senses, the Elements sacrifice all of their defense.
I think it would be best if we all just covered up for now.
How?
When did you take these?
Here is 500 kowloons.
Thanks so much!
Put me down for one!
Me too!
Stop it!
Do not sell any more of those!
Zessica.
What are you doing all the way over here?
Nothing!
I am not doing anything!
Try saying horrible ten times fast.
Horrible horrible horble hobble holeble hole hole...
I hate holes!
I am going to fill them all!
